vote.title: A public hearing to consider authorizing a public hearing to amend (1) the relocation of certain detached non-premise signs provisions in 51A-7.307; (2) the digital displayed on certain detached non-premise sign provisions in Section 51A-7.308; and (3) the non-conformance and enforcement procedures in Division 51A-7.700 of the Dallas City Code (This is a hearing to consider the request to authorize the hearing and not the ordinance amending the Dallas City Code at this time) - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
